<item>
            <title>[FELIX-3130] Nested composites throws StackOverflowError on instantiation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-3130</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following metadata.xml describes a composite with another nested composite. Instantiating &quot;composite-external&quot; throws a StackOverflowError &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot; encoding=&quot;UTF-8&quot;?&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;ipojo xmlns=&quot;org.apache.felix.ipojo&quot; xmlns:c=&quot;org.apache.felix.ipojo.composite&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;	&amp;lt;component name=&quot;comp-a&quot; classname=&quot;test.ComponentAImpl&quot; /&amp;gt;	&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;	&amp;lt;c:composite name=&quot;composite-internal&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
		&amp;lt;instance component=&quot;comp-a&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
	&amp;lt;/c:composite&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;	&amp;lt;c:composite name=&quot;composite-external&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
		&amp;lt;instance component=&quot;composite-internal&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
	&amp;lt;/c:composite&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;/ipojo&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
